==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Somnial
<hw>Som"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>somnialis</ets> dream bringing, fr. <ets>somnium</ets> dream, fr.
<ets>somnus</ets> sleep.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to sleep or
dreams.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>somnial</qex> magic superinduced on, without suspending,
the active powers of the mind.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Somniative</ent>⟦br⟧
